{"title":"terminal proxy","uid":"99549990e3a692a5bd343420bd9e2a64","slug":"powershell","date":"2023-03-20T08:10:22.000Z","updated":"2024-07-28T15:50:23.091Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/powershell.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/terminal.png","content":"<p>terminal is a task automation and configuration management program from Microsoft, consisting of a command-line shell and the associated scripting language.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Powershell-Show-Proxy\"><a href=\"#Powershell-Show-Proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Powershell Show Proxy\"></a>Powershell Show Proxy</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">netsh winhttp show proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Powershell-Set-Proxy\"><a href=\"#Powershell-Set-Proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Powershell Set Proxy\"></a>Powershell Set Proxy</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">netsh winhttp <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> proxy 127.0.0.1:10808</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 临时设置代理，关闭powershell会清掉</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$env</span>:HTTP_PROXY=<span class=\"string\">&quot;http://127.0.0.1:10808&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Powershell-Cancle-Proxy\"><a href=\"#Powershell-Cancle-Proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Powershell Cancle Proxy\"></a>Powershell Cancle Proxy</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">netsh winhttp reset proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Cmd-Temporary-Set-Proxy\"><a href=\"#Cmd-Temporary-Set-Proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Cmd Temporary Set Proxy\"></a>Cmd Temporary Set Proxy</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> http_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># cancel proxy for localhost</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> no_proxy=localhost, 127.0.0.1, ::1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"terminal is a task automation and configuration management program from Microsof...","permalink":"/post/powershell","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":565,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"PROXY","slug":"PROXY","count":4,"path":"api/categories/PROXY.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"terminal","slug":"terminal","count":2,"path":"api/tags/terminal.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Powershell-Show-Proxy\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Powershell Show Proxy</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Powershell-Set-Proxy\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Powershell Set Proxy</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Powershell-Cancle-Proxy\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Powershell Cancle Proxy</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Cmd-Temporary-Set-Proxy\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Cmd Temporary Set Proxy</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Kidwen","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com